text: Prime Location Near conveniently located next to Longwood Medical and all the Fenway Triangle has to offer including the Time Out Market, Star Market Grocery Store, Target and SO much more. This Charming studio has nice natural light and great views. No Undergrads - Studio with separated kitchen & breakfast nook- Tons of closet space- Additional storage in basement- Laundry in basement- Heat is included- Hot water & electric not included- New windows- Beautiful view- Hardwood floors- Tons of natural light
